-- This is a test control file

test_name 	 repeated-manifest-bit-array
test_description A class repeatedly creates a manifest array with a single element of type BIT 32.  Executing the system results in a segmentation fault or run-time panic after a larg enumber of iterations.  If garbage collection is off or the BIT 32 array element is not a local entity, the system executes correctly.

copy_sub 	 Ace $TEST Ace
copy_raw 	 test.e  $CLUSTER test.e
compile_melted
compile_result 	 ok

execute_work	 NONE exec_output1 50000
execute_result	 ok
compare		 exec_output1 output

test_end
